Class SongRecord

  • java.lang.Object
    • pkg1.SongRecord
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable

    public class SongRecord
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable
    The SongRecord class is used to create song objects It contains the data fields: title, artist, minutes, seconds The method implements Cloneable because the class implements a clone method for SongRecord objects
    Version:
    1, July 12 2016
    Author:
    Jonathan Mathai
